      "text": [
        " يُحَدُّ قَاذِفُ اللَّقِيطِ وَ يُحَدُّ قَاذِفُ ابْنِ الْمُلَاعَنَةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, form Ibn Mahboub, from one of his companions, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘The slanderer of the bastard would be penalised (by the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>)), and the slanderer of the son of a woman cursed by her husband would be penalised (by the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>))’."
        ]
